"""
pacmangr: an animated terminal package manager for mixed Linux systems.

It autodetects package managers already present on the host, including distro
managers, language package managers, Flatpak, and local AppImages. Search/list
operations run inside curses when a manager exposes parseable output. Install,
remove, update, and version-list operations run without replacing the native
package managers underneath.
"""

